show.description: "Hidden Billionaire" follows Rohit, a boy from the slums , who rises from poverty and betrayal to reclaim his legacy as the heir to Kulkarni Industries, wielding a mysterious power to protect his family from ruthless enemies. This gripping tale of resilience, revenge, and reunion unfolds over decades, blending emotional drama with supernatural intrigue.
